[{"id":"VH904303","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><include href=\"../Passage/VH905001.qti.xml\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\"></include></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">What does Weijie plan to do next semester?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH904303_rubric","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<p class=\"introduction passage-intro\">Read this letter from a pen pal.</p>\n\n<div class=\"passage\">\n<div class=\"letter letter_type:informal style:1\">\n<p class=\"letter_salutation\">明華：</p>\n\n<div class=\"letter_body\">\n<p class=\"passage_para\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;好久沒有寫信了，你還好嗎？我自從來到美國上高中，每天都很忙：要忙著學習、做作業，為了將來申請大學還要參加不同的課外活動。我已經加入了中文俱樂部、數學俱樂部等。本來也想加入辯論隊，但是我的英文還不夠好，所以我要努力把英語學好，爭取下學期加入辯論隊。除了這些以外，我還做義工，有時下午和週末在藝術之家教小朋友畫畫。你看，我在美國上學比在中國上學更忙！我現在最大的享受就是週末能睡個懶覺。</p>\n\n<p class=\"passage_para\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;你呢？快要畢業了吧？有時間就給我回個信。</p>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"letter_closing\">祝你一切順利！</p>\n\n<div class=\"letter_signature\">\n<p class=\"signature_line text-center\">偉傑</p>\n\n<p class=\"signature_line text-center\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 五月八日</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"passage\">\n<div class=\"letter letter_type:informal style:1\">\n<p class=\"letter_salutation\">明华：</p>\n\n<div class=\"letter_body\">\n<p class=\"passage_para\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;好久没有写信了，你还好吗？我自从来到美国上高中，每天都很忙：要忙着学习、做作业，为了将来申请大学还要参加不同的课外活动。我已经加入了中文俱乐部、数学俱乐部等。本来也想加入辩论队，但是我的英文还不够好，所以我要努力把英语学好，争取下学期加入辩论队。除了这些以外，我还做义工，有时下午和周末在艺术之家教小朋友画画。你看，我在美国上学比在中国上学更忙！我现在最大的享受就是周末能睡个懒觉。</p>\n\n<p class=\"passage_para\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;你呢？快要毕业了吧？有时间就给我回个信。</p>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"letter_closing\">祝你一切顺利！</p>\n\n<div class=\"letter_signature\">\n<p class=\"signature_line text-center\">伟杰</p>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"letter_date text-center\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 五月八日</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}],"choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Apply for college</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Join a debate club</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Take a science class</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Volunteer at a museum</p>"],"answer":1}]